    class Barcode_Tracker_Factory
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.android.gms.vision.MultiProcessor.Factory<com.google.android.gms.vision.barcode.Barcode>
    Factory for creating a tracker and associated graphic to be associated with a new barcode. The multi-processor uses this factory to create barcode trackers as needed -- one for each barcode.
